1. Theoretical models                                             7240 1451
 The POD code is based on the spherical optical model, the        7240 1451
distorted-wave Born approximaiton (DWBA), one-component exciton   7240 1451
preequilibrium model, and the Hauser-Feshbach-Moldauer statis-    7240 1451
tical model.  With the preequilibrim model, semi-empirical        7240 1451
pickup and knockout process can be taken into account for         7240 1451
composite-particle emission.  The gamma-ray emission from the     7240 1451
compound nucleus can be calculated within the framework of the    7240 1451
exciton model.  The code is capable of reading in particle        7240 1451
transmission coefficients calculated by separate spherical or     7240 1451
coupled-channel optical model code.                               7240 1451
                                                                  7240 1451
